description.narrative:
The objective of this project is to support the communities in which MLR Forestal operates and employees by:
(i) securing food and sanitation products for children and the most vulnerable;
(ii) supporting the indigenous populations in the area of Bonanza with the provision of food and sanitation packages and prevent them from leaving their ancestral territories;
(iii) offering support to the most vulnerable during the isolation period in the pandemic;
(iv) supporting the local health centres with disinfection products, PPEs, portable hand washing devices, in order to ensure the highest degree of protection to the health staff;
(v) ongoing awareness and information campaign.

